code: public Tuple6Builder<T0, T1, T2, T3, T4, T5> add(T0 value0, T1 value1, T2 value2, T3 value3, T4 value4, T5 value5) {     tuples.add(new Tuple6<>(value0, value1, value2, value3, value4, value5)).     return this. }
